  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening Local Mechanisms for Conflict Prevention and Resolution in Burundi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to improve capacities of formal and informal law enforcement actors to prevent and resolve conflicts related to increasedmigration and repatriation; improve access to rehabilitation and traditional healing services for community members traumatized by psychological and physical abuse; set up spaces for dialogues to promotecommunity reconciliation and social cohesion; and improve the administrative and procedural capacity of law enforcement officials to increase internal accountability for the prevention of conflicts.</narrative>
  </description>
